configured cadence and boundaries |
+| Review Priority | Optional queue-ordering policy output; never a measure of human value |
+| Profile readiness | Purpose-specific coverage of required profile information |
+| Topic Pack | Versioned reusable set of typed profile fields and sections |
+| Field state | Explicit epistemic state such as verified, unknown, declined, stale, or conflicting |
+| Resource | First-class file, URL, calendar item, email reference, photo, map, or document link |
+| Membership | Dated Person-to-Organization or Person-to-Group association |
 | Interaction | Meaningful communication, meeting, note, commitment, or source-linked event |
 | Event | Planned or recorded activity with attendees and operational requirements |
 | Attendance | A person's recorded participation in an event |
